57.1	Neill_Blomkamp	Neill Blomkamp	Neill Blomkamp (born 17 September 1979) is a South African-Canadian film and advertisement writer and director. Blomkamp employs a documentary-style, hand-held, cinéma vérité technique, blending naturalistic and photo-realistic computer-generated effects. He is best known as the co-writer and director of critically acclaimed District 9, his only feature film to date. He is based out of Vancouver, British Columbia.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ad/NeillBlomkampCCJuly09.jpg/220px-NeillBlomkampCCJuly09.jpg
